Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Mysterious Transfer Student, Ryuji Otogi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anzu, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, what's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandfather doesn't seem too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's not in a very good mood these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd never ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sugoroku Mutou, at age 72,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am facing the biggest crisis of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My store is in danger of going out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new game shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gathered the best games from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got good deals on almost everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're rumored to be selling the latest, most popular games!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The latest games, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for grandpa, but it's got {\i1}my{\i0} interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Revolutionary New Game: D.D.M.\N On Sale Tomorrow!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of game this "D.D.M." is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yugi Mutou...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The{\i0} rumored one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's supposedly a revolutionist when it comes to Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat {\i1}the{\i0} Pegasus in Duelist Kingdom and won the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Although I doubt the Duel Monsters champ would be beaten that easily.\N- God, Yugi! I saw that look in your eyes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do doubt he's a match when it comes to D.D.M.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'll steal something important from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll surely force him into the D.D.M. arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure you're only aiming to promote D.D.M.'s appeal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please mind to your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat Yugi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and once D.D.M.'s name roars across the world, you'll get your cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Otogi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll beat you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've prepared a ton of games to steal your gaming title from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new game shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's not doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's gonna become a really tough rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems they've made some new game called D.D.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dungeon Dice Monsters", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... do you know that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a flyer for it in today's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Jounouchi, you read the newspaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read them while {\i1}delivering{\i0} them at my part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't part-time jobs prohibited here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna here that from {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have {\i1}special permission{\i0} to work for my tuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I spent all the cash prize Yugi won for me on Shizuka's operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Shizuka-chan's operation date's been decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor took a look,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and said her eyes can be fully restored after the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really great, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah~! Cool~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show us one more time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time I'll do it with six dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow~! That's so cool~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's {\i1}this{\i0} guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is he from your guys' class?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he's a new transfer student named Ryuji Otogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that answers your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand guys like him who use cheap tricks to pick up girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just jealous of whoever's more popular than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type of guy who keeps a well-sharpened katana in its sheath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't {\i1}need{\i0} to show off my talents to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually {\i1}have{\i0} talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you watching
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we went to Duelist Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amateur who won by pure luck, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock if off, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My talents were awakened on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My talents as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're good at Duel Monsters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a little while back, but did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy named Keith Howard was the U.S. champion and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was one hell of a strong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he sure put up a good fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he couldn't stand up to {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally bragging...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just drawn every katana he's got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope ya get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Duelist Kingdom champion, Yugi Mutou-kun, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the rumors about your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard any rumors about the young talent, Katsuya Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you like to play a game with me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can show me what this "young talent" thing is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this die and this cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what kind of game this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yeah!\N -You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I beat this Otogi bastard, I'll get all his fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do you think I can move the die
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into my right hand without touching the cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it obvious that's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you have some kind of telepathic abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way you can get to the die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was talking, the die should have vanished from the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you see for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the die right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just moved the die to my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't touch the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you freakin' {\i1}kidding{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who lost, by winning using such a low method!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a Duel Monsters match fair-and-square!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a condition I'd like to set before we start the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take whatever you throw at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have my own deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-What?! That's not fair!\N -That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you wanna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we Duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we open new packs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and build our decks from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reasonable condition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they aren't the normal cards you're used to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're bound to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's a ton of cards Jounouchi-kun doesn't even know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doubting my skills after taking Pegasus' tournament head on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it like {\i1}that{\i0}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to make this better than that last game we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, how'd you like to become my {\i1}dog{\i0} for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if {\i1}I{\i0} win, I'll be taking that little cheering section over there as my fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-What?! That's terrible!\N -You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare belittle a match between men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, you should just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I'd lose to this cheating bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm the same guy who won the Best 8 in the City District League!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}know{\i0} that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep your mouth shut and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match will be held after school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hold it at the Duel Ring in my newly opened game shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you guys to watch your friend's "cool battle" as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi-kun, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what could he be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm really pumped now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay him back good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Jounouchi really be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya think {\i1}anyone{\i0} can stop that idiot from bragging so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head's starting to swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, welcome~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Otogi-chan's {\i1}special{\i0} opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. So you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way to the Duel Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose any packs you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the new cards to make your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm lucky as hell to get these good cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same Ring Kaiba Land has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more fun to Duel when everyone can watch us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel is being broadcast across the world over the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will bear witness as the once-proud Duelist Kingdom runner up loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice face you're making, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the "Otogi Girls" into the "Jounouchi Girls"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall protect you gals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cool~! He's stunning~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni Tank T-34!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my turn's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your superb talent as a Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need {\i1}you{\i0} to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got a card with an awesome Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Monster it destroys becomes an Equipment Card, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play Sword Hunter in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunter Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni Tank is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni Tank will become an Equipment Card on Sword Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his Attack Power goes up by 200 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~! No~! Otogi-kun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Jounouchi's not doing too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's {\i1}that{\i0}, Otogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't a match for {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I would expect from you, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too late to realize that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Bat in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then place another set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna get out of this by playing on the defensive side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charging Swordhorn Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank {\i1}goodness{\i0} I placed it in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it {\i1}was{\i0} in Defense Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Charging Swordhorn Beast smashes right through their guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the player receives the difference as damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are something else, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my Monster won't be going to the Graveyard alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Murder-Suicide"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi was way too naive there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did that on purpose to make the game more interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you fell for it hook, line and sinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may seem that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but Otogi-kun's the one controlling this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty cheap trick back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still way to early to get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time I play a tough Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make my counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set 1 card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Spike Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try harder, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like the tortoise and the hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! If you lose, you're gonna become Otogi's {\i1}dog{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh snap, I forgot about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time I get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card stands no chance if I play {\i1}this{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, your Life's practically drizzled away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi-kun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys go into Defense Mode the turn after you use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now Otogi's Life is down to 50!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My victory's set!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better get ready, Jounouchi Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~ No~! Otogi-kun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't agree with the Jounouchi Girls part,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but go for it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! You're one step away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has such little Life remaining, yet Otogi-kun looks so calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he still planning something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-You have to focus!\N -This match is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~! Hey~! Jounouchi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Super Dimension Fighter Vic Viper in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play the Magic Card, Limiter Removal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vic Viper powers up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got {\i1}2400{\i0} Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Goblins are screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be beaten in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic, Meteor Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what Effect does that card have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're the runner up of the championship
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and {\i1}still{\i0} don't know these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as a Magic version of the Charging Swordhorn Beast you used earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it attacks a Monster in Defense Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Attack Points of the Monster equipped with this card
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are greater than the Defense Points of the Monster it attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the difference in points comes directly out of the opponent's Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say {\i1}what{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viv Viper Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, you did it~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi got way too overconfident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to keep your promise, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be my dog for the next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I grown rusty since the Duelist Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried harder than my own skill limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I grew better, to achieve my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I gotten in over my head now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this be as is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, just stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi! \N-Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my {\i1}dog{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only talk if I say you can do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-That's just...!\N -That's just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say "That hurt", you say "woof"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you bark out a "woof" for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm, that sure fits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"W-Woof!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts messing with my friend right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're facing {\i1}me{\i0}, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, you'll let Jounouchi go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like to change the game this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be facing each other with Dungeon Dice Monsters, D.D.M.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose to me, I'll be taking your "King of Duelists" title for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll swear to never play Duel Monsters again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi brought this on himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, don't do it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't break our friendship with a {\i1}game{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you up on your D.D.M. match!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,140)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you accepted to play Otogi-kun in D.D.M.!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you even promised to never play Duel Monsters again if you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi doesn't even know how the play the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Otogi-kun knows all the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why did he go through all this trouble to lure Yugi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showdown! Dungeon Dice Monsters!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
